  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core Gameplay</strong><br>In the city, titanium alloy coins will continuously appear. Collect as many coins as possible before your energy runs out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also talk to other robots to restore your energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the collected coins to upgrade the core attributes of the robot on the main interface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Controls</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use \"W, A, S, D\" to control the robot's movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press the \"space\" key to jump.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold \"shift\" to sprint.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press \"E\" to interact and talk.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Core Gameplay</strong><br>In the city, titanium alloy coins will continuously appear. Collect as many coins as possible before your energy runs out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also talk to other robots to restore your energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the collected coins to upgrade the core attributes of the robot on the main interface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Controls</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use \"W, A, S, D\" to control the robot's movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press the \"space\" key to jump.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold \"shift\" to sprint.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press \"E\" to interact and talk.</p></li></ul>",
